{{Top|leg|title=''Senate''-class transport}}
'''''Senate''-class transports''' was a multi-purpose [[Transport/Legends|transport]] used by [[Senator/Legends|senators]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] shortly before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. One such transport was also used to carry [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] to a transfer dock in the [[Orbit/Legends|orbit]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], where they boarded the [[Starship/Legends|starship]] ''[[Star Sea Flower]]''.

